control of our health.

00:00:47.300 --> 00:00:48.818 align:middle line:84%
We're handing control
of our health,

00:00:48.818 --> 00:00:50.860 align:middle line:84%
and our thoughts, and our
beliefs to other people

00:00:50.860 --> 00:00:52.030 align:middle line:90%
