yourself in this ocean of bliss

00:04:10.180 --> 00:04:11.495 align:middle line:90%
when you're there.

00:04:11.495 --> 00:04:13.120 align:middle line:84%
Now, what starts
happening in your body

00:04:13.120 --> 00:04:15.400 align:middle line:90%
