00:04:15.400 --> 00:04:17.200 align:middle line:90%
It is not high adrenaline.

00:04:17.200 --> 00:04:18.940 align:middle line:90%
It's high DHEA.

00:04:18.940 --> 00:04:20.410 align:middle line:90%
It's high oxytocin.

00:04:20.410 --> 00:04:23.200 align:middle line:84%
